about_me_paragraph: I am a Junior Front-end Developer with 2 years of experience in HTML5, CSS3, StyledComponents, TailwindCSS, ReactJS, TypeScript, NextJS, React Native, and JavaScript. I currently work at Lionsoft, where I develop modern and responsive interfaces. I'm in my fifth semester of Systems Analysis and Development at Facens, and in addition to front-end development, I am studying Node.js, SQL, Express, and Fastify, with the goal of becoming a Full Stack Developer and improving my skills in back-end development.
